Hello, I am Marcel, 20 years old. This channel will only consist of BeamNG Drive. I also want to bring quality videos.

The Process

- Recording the Clips with oCam! 3-5 hours, sometimes longer
- Editing & synchronizing clips with music & addition of captions / sound effects with Premiere Pro (1-3 hours)
- Descriptions, Thumbnails etc. (30 min)

Game Info:
BeamNG.drive is a realistic, immersive driving game offering near-limitless possibilities. Our soft-body physics engine simulates every component of a vehicle in real time, resulting in realistic, dynamic behavior

My Upload is random! :)

Please subscribe and like my videos when you like this channel thanks! :D

description:
Hello, I'm Andy. My goal is to create entertaining videos mostly, but not only, for people who love cars & crashes. 

All the videos you'll find in this channel are recorded & edited by me and my sidekick, George, who helps with parts of the editing.
This channel is our full-time job. We're devoting a minimum of 100 hours per week to bring you the best BeamNG drive videos.

How we work:

Creating these videos is a lot harder & time consuming than you might think but it is what makes us and, hopefully, you happy!
We are playing BeamNG.drive, a PC Game featuring the ultimate soft-body physics and realism. 

The process, step by step:

- Recording the clips with Action! (10-15 hours, sometimes 15+)
- Editing & synchronizing the clips with music & addition of captions / sound effects - Premiere Pro (5-10 hours)  
- Descriptions, Thumbnails etc.  (2 hours)

We’re uploading 4 Videos per week on Tuesday, Thursday, Saturday & Sunday. Stay up to date by Subscribing!
Thank you :)

I'm also a Mild Gamer playing Minecraft and more!

Using the original analog masters whenever possible, the company will create thoughtfully produced, detailed packaging with a commitment to preservation and a meticulous devotion to quality. Further, Craft Recordings will continue to partner with artists and estates to preserve and enhance the musical heritage of these landmark recordings and compositions.

description:
Platinum-selling rapper Herbert “G Herbo” Wright has endured a season of close calls and losing several of his closest friends to senseless gun violence in his native Chicago. All of this was channeled into his critically acclaimed double album, Survivor’s Remorse in 2022 which Rolling Stone called, “another potent look into his rattled, conflicted psyche that also doubles as a celebration of his 10-year run as one of the most enduring young rappers to come out of Chicago’s drill scene.” Following up from his 2023 mixtape, Strictly For My Fans 2, and earning  Platinum and Gold plaques for Nardo Wick’s “Who Want Smoke” and his late friend Young Dolph’s “One Scale” that same year, Herbo aims to reach his full potential as an artist with his celebratory offering for the summertime, Big Swerv. The album is executive produced by longtime collaborators Southside and Big Oz.
G Herbo's four albums,”PTSD,” “25,” “Swervo,” and his debut, “Humble Beast” all reached the Billboard Top 200 chart.

Welcome to King Von's OFFICIAL channel. Subscribe here for all music videos, audio releases, and official content from King Von. 

King Von was born Dayvon Bennett on Chicago's South Side and raised in the crime-ridden O Block neighbourhood. After beginning to rap in 2018, King Von caught the interest of Chicago flagbearer, Lil Durk, and was welcomed into the Only the Family collective. Following up to his early single "Problems", King Von broke onto the map with "Crazy Story", which was streamed over 200 million times. This was followed with his debut album, "Grandson, Vol. 1", which broke out onto the Billboard 200. Be sure to follow King Von on his socials and streaming platforms to stay tuned for the come up.

Hello Everyone,

Myself Maash, Welcome to my channel; mostly I am engaged in creation of this channel making racing and crashing videos for this channel using Beaming Drive.
My mission is to bring entertaining videos for all who loves cars, races & crashes.

Everyday I try to come up with interesting ideas for this channel which are edited and recorded by myself using Bandicam.

Creating, recording, scripting and editing these videos is a lot harder and time consuming than you might think but this is what makes me happy and hopefully makes you happy as well.
The Process:
• Recording with clips with action (7-8 Hours sometimes 10+ hours)
   Using Bandicam
• Editing the clips with music and adding of captions / sound effects (4-5 hours)
   Using Adobe Premiere Pro
• Beaming Modes downloaded from  https://www.beamng.com https://www.modland.net 
   I upload twice a week, every Friday and Monday.

Stay up to date by being a part of this adventure.

Subscribe and stay tuned!!

description:
George Harrison, MBE (25 February 1943 – 29 November 2001) was an influential English rock guitarist, singer, songwriter, author and sitarist best known as the lead guitarist of The Beatles. Following the band's demise, Harrison had a successful career as a solo artist and later as part of the Traveling Wilburys super group where he was known as both Nelson Wilbury and Spike Wilbury. He was also a film producer, with his production company Handmade Films, involving people as diverse as Madonna and the members of Monty Python. From an initial exposure whilst a member of the Beatles, he maintained a high public profile regarding his religious and spiritual life.

February 25th marks what would have been George’s 75th birthday. In love and remembrance, CONCERT FOR GEORGE will be reissued on February 23rd, as a Deluxe Edition Box Set, a 4-LP Box Set, plus new CD/DVD and CD/Blu-ray combo packages.

-- Chris K the Lightning Hunter

description:
WW2 Flight simulator compilations!

I enjoy playing IL-2 Sturmovik Great Battles primarily, because I believe it is the best WW2 flight simulator for the following reasons;

 Firstly, the damage modelling in IL-2 is comprehensive.  Enabling me to compile realistic plane crash compilations. 
 Secondly IL-2 offers a broad spectrum of WW2 aircraft to fly. From single engine fighters to larger bomber variants. 
 Thirdly IL-2 has a rich online multi-player community. In addition to that it has a great Online Forum community.
 Finally it is constantly updated by the devs.

Creating plane crash compilations with IL-2 Is probably my favorite. However, I also have fun creating Flight Sim compilations 
on a variety of areas. Some of those include. Bailout compilations, crash landing compilations, engine fire compilations and 
Ground Attack compilations to name but a few.

Welcome to my channel!

My name is Martin and this is an aviation channel. I started taking pictures of planes in 2005 and in 2011 I tested the video function of my new DSLR camera. I was very surprised by the hugh amount of feedback I received within the past four years. I never thought I could reach such a hugh amount of people just by sharing my passion on youtube. 

On this channel you can find Aviation videos, made by myself. My "homebase" is Düsseldorf but I like to travel around a lot. That` s why I also upload videos from St. Martin, St. Barth, Skiathos, Amsterdam and other airpots which offer interesting oportunities to create interesting footage. I prefere to make videos of rare planes like Ilyushins, Tupolevs, old Boeings and classic Douglas planes.

Welcome to Foolish Driver! Our mission is to entertain you guys with an awesome channel that celebrates the fun in crash physics, with a whole host of different themed videos.

I spend 50-70 hours per week making these videos. It takes about 8-10 hours on average to make a video - every single scenes is set up by hand by me, the camera angles, focus depth, focus length, simulation speed and lighting all adjusted by me, then it's recorded, 40GB of footage is edited, painstakingly synchronized to music and sound effects added by hand. 

How we work:

Creating these videos is a lot harder & time consuming than you might think but it is what makes us and, hopefully, you happy!

NoLimitAutobahn is a German Youtube channel for people who love cars more than her wife.

description: Long before BAD ACTRESS burst on to their local music scene in 2018, each of the members had been clocking up performing, writing and recording experience with different bands of different styles. In bringing all this together they quickly established an extensive catalogue of solid original material, rooted in ‘good time’ blues and hard rock and written to impress. They use each and every one of their live performances to showcase this material and soon bagged a few awards for their efforts. Since then, they have been delighting crowds wherever they go. They’ve supported top acts such as Gun, Electric Boys and Hardline, and completed two UK tours supporting Marco Mendoza (Whitesnake, Dead Daisies, Journey). They’ve played festivals and headline shows the length and breadth of the UK, including headlining the second stage at the Hard Rock Hell Sleaze Fest 2022 in the Sheffield O2. BAD ACTRESS is on a mission to be part of the reason people keep going to see live rock shows.

description:
The MIT Museum engages the wider community with MIT’s science, technology, and other areas of scholarship in ways that will best serve the nation and the world in the 21st century.

The MIT Museum fulfills this mission by collecting and preserving objects that are significant in the life of MIT; creating exhibits and programs that are firmly rooted in MIT’s areas of endeavor; and engaging MIT faculty, staff, and students with the wider community.

The Museum is dedicated to collecting, preserving, and exhibiting materials that serve as a resource for the study and interpretation of the intellectual, educational, and social history of the Massachusetts Institute of Technology and its role in the development of modern science and technology. The Museum stands alone among university museums in its focus on the impact on society of the research, the teaching, and the scientific innovations of its parent institution.

See website for programs, exhibitions, and events.

description:
The Royal Microscopical Society - at the forefront of microscopy since 1839
The RMS is dedicated to furthering the science of microscopy.  It does that through a wide range of activities that support research and education in microscopy, and through enabling microscopists to make advances and developments in microscopy, cytometry and imaging.  

Activities of the society include dissemination of research and news through publications and communication, the organisation of conference, training and networking events, the provision of outreach resources including resources for schools, and through supporting careers through awards and bursaries.

We are a truly international society, and welcome members from all countries and backgrounds that are interested in microscopes and the science of microscopy.

The RMS is a not for profit organisation and is a registered Charity, under the Charities Act 2011.

Kijk mee bij De Haagse Ballonnenboer en zijn ballonfiguren !

Vind jij ballonfiguren leuk om te krijgen en zou je zelf eens met deze gekke en lange ballonnen aan de slag willen ?

Leer de basisfiguren, diverse ballontechnieken, welke ballonnen je kunt gebruiken en nog veel meer!

Magische acts, ballonnen shows, Tips en Tricks, teveel om op te noemen.
De Ballonnenboer heeft al 600 video's op zijn kanaal, . 

Veel plezier en heb je vragen, de Haagse Ballonnenboer hoort ze graag !
Word * ABONNEE * van mijn kanaal en help mee om de  * 3500 * abonnees te halen !
Ik vind het SUPER TOF in ieder geval dat je mee kijkt !!

Je kunt mij ook vinden op TikTok, Facebook en Instagram !!

Texashighdef was founded and managed in 2008 by my uncle. Sadly, he passed away unexpectedly in July 2023. While his legal name was Lindsay, he was affectionately known as Duke to his friends and family. He entrusted me, his niece and namesake, with continuing the legacy of this channel. I am dedicated to preserving and enhancing Texashighdef’s tradition of providing calming and relaxing content, as he has done for the past 15 years. As I am still relatively new to this role, I would greatly appreciate any feedback and suggestions. 

Much love, Lindsay O’Connor. 

Welcome to the TexasHighDef Channel.  I created and own all rights to 99.99% of all the content on this channel. All videos are shot on a camcorder and are not just a picture and a loop. I try my best to bring you the very best rain and sleep videos on You Tube.
Thanks for stopping by.
Duke
